{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocationannotationview\/update"]}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"update","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this method to update the appearance of the user location annotation. This","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method is called by the associated map view when it has determined that the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"user location annotation needs to be updated. This can happen in response to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"user interaction, a change in the user’s location, when the user tracking mode","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"changes, or when the viewport changes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"During user interaction with the map, this method may be called many","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"times to update the user location annotation. Therefore, your implementation of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this method should be as lightweight as possible to avoid negatively affecting","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"performance.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","style":"note"}]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"update","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"update"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/m